 as expected. The very important role that bug-killers play in 
 crop production is pointed to/showed by the positive and 
 significant coefficients on the fungus-killer, carbofuran 
 and foliar insecticide (numbers that change/things that change). Output-constant 
 own-price elasticities of demand (equal to /3; - 1) 
