 In comparison, the guesses of the ability to stretch of cost 
 with respect to health received/got by Antle and Pingali 
 in their study of two rice producing areas of the 
 Philippines ranged from -0.13 to -0.36. 
 
 As explained by Antle et al. (1994), it is important in 
 guessing production models with bug-killers to account for the large number of different chemicals 
 that are used by farmers that show changing/different degress 
 of effectiveness in controlling pests. To control for different bug-killer quality, the fungus-killer amount and price 
 and the plants pest insecticide amount and price 
 were quality (changed to make better/changed to fit new conditions) using the (related to feeling pleasure) procedure 
 described by Antle et al. (1994). Expected yield y 
 was guessed as the (described the future) value of a moving backward 
 of actual yield on the amount of seed potato spread around, a 
 set of dummy (numbers that change/things that change) pointing to/showing soil types and 
 (rain, snow, etc.), the height of the field, and its area. 
 
 4. Effects/results/suggestions 
 The limit/guideline guesses of the cost function are 
 all (meaningful numbers) and point to/show decreasing 
 
 204 
 
 J.M. Antle et al. /Agricultural Money flow 18 (1998) 199-207 
 
 The health production function limits/guidelines are 
 highly significant and point to/show, as expected, that 
 farmers with higher verbal intelligence scores (c 1 
 and c2 ) also have higher neurobehavioral function. 
 The total amount of carbofuran applied during the 
 season has the guessed negative effect on neurobehavioral function. 
 Combining the cost function and the health equation, we see that higher neurobehavioral function of 
 farm managers lowers average production cost, while 
 
 increased use of the insecticide carbofuran increases 
 crop production but lowers neurobehavioral function. 
 To test the net effects of a change in carbofuran 
 use, we tested out the model over a range of carbofuran prices (from 50% below the watched/followed mean price 
 to 200% above it). To (ask lots of questions about/try to find the truth about) the effects of the 
 (wasting very little while working or producing something) of other choice restrictions on bug-killers, the 
 (testing out) was performed with the tax charged on 
 carbofuran alone and with it (forced (on people)/caused an inconvenient situation) on all bug-killers. To (ask lots of questions about/try to find the truth about) the importance of the health 
 
