 of the relationship is higher when the effect of health 
 on working well is taken into account. This figure 
 also shows that there is little difference between a 
 tax on carbofuran only and a tax on all bug-killers in 
 terms of the health results. This is because there is 
 little substitution between carbofuran and other bug-killer inputs. 
